Using the measures of BEHAVIORit above, we compare ESG funds to non-ESG funds by estimating the following series of regressions:
1BEHAVIORijt=β0+β1ESGit+β2Controlsit+ηjt+εit\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
